               Linux installation

1. Install OpenJDK Java 7 using update manager of your distro
   unless you hvae it already installed. Easy check is typing 'java' in
   terminal window.

2. Unpack MediaChest archive, type in a terminal window
unzip MediaChest-NNN.zip  (MediaChest-200.zip)
or you can do it double clicking MediaChest-NNN.zip in graphical environment
and select extract
3. Go to MediaChest directory and type
./MediaChest
you can run it also double clicking MediaChest in graphical environment
chmod 755 MediaChest can required